DIAGNOSTICS
  E0250: conflict target (slug) is not a unique key of `Note`
  E0251: the `on conflict update` branch assigns the conflict column `label`
  E0253: `on conflict` is not allowed on the @soft_delete model `Tag`
SCHEMA
model Page  table=page
  id: Id
  path: text  unique
  hits: int
model Note  table=note
  id: Id
  slug: text
  body: text
model Tag  table=tag  soft_delete=deleted_at(timestamp)
  id: Id
  deleted_at: timestamp?
  label: text  unique
shape PageRow from Page
shape NoteRow from Note
shape TagRow from Tag
mutation record_hit  ret=Page
mutation upsert_note  ret=Note
mutation touch_tag  ret=Tag
